divs: Sighting DetailsWhile stopped on the side of the road (off or rt 80) to take some photos of area. We notices a fleet of objects in the sky (moving from north(northeast) heading South(southwest) over 70 objects kept changing formation (mostly in pairs) forming half-circular shape to "L" shape and other random formations. I was able to take several photos of the event with my professional 16.6 Mega-pixel camera and a 100mm lens. Even though objects are not 100% clear, once i zoom in on the image, I can come to a definite conclusion that these were un-winged objects (spheres).
trends: There has been one other sighting in Grantsville
There were no other sightings in Grantsville on or around November 25th 2008
Summary: Multiple spheres moving and changing formation.
